		<region region-id="137" left="12" top="44.25" width="468" height="42" align-x="12" align-y="54" show-border="false" show-highlight="false" is-protected="true" z-order="0" background-color="inherit" tag="">
			<text use-page-width="false" push-down="false" lock-width="true">
				<p style="Normal" margin-left="inherit" margin-right="inherit" text-indent="inherit" text-align="inherit" list-style-type="inherit" tabs="inherit">- 'dt' should be very small in order to achive higher numerical accuracy (Not related to sampeling rate).</p>
				<p style="Normal" margin-left="inherit" margin-right="inherit" text-indent="inherit" text-align="inherit" list-style-type="inherit" tabs="inherit">- Rotation direction sign is derived by the right hand rule.</p>
				<p style="Normal" margin-left="inherit" margin-right="inherit" text-indent="inherit" text-align="inherit" list-style-type="inherit" tabs="inherit">- The new State-Matrix is solved by multiplying the State-Matrix by the Delta-Matrix (R<f family="Arial" charset="0" size="10">
						<inlineAttr font-weight="normal" font-style="normal" underline="false" line-through="false">
							<sub>new </sub>
						</inlineAttr>
					</f>= R<b>
						<sup>.</sup>
					</b>W) </p>
			</text>
		</region>
